Assert the <"ratePerKG"> <"serviceOwner"> and rate for <"regular"> and <"express"> method of delivery options

elements.name: To test the delivery method and price updated in order summary with the selection of delivery method

steps.name: Landing on the Shopping page
Assert the logo of the retailer
Items are listed in the shopping cart
Click on CheckOut option
Assert it is redirected to the delivery selection page
Assert the logo of the retailer
Enter the delivery information
Enter the delivery address with <"pinCode">
Select on the <"deliveryMethod">
Assert the <"price"> of the delivery method
Assert Under order summary <"deliveryMethod"> and its <"price"> are updated correctly
Assert the total of the order summary

elements.name: To test the checking out of items in cart

steps.name: Landing on the Shopping page
Assert the logo of the retailer
Assert the items are listed in the shopping cart

elements.name: To test the items and its details are non editable

steps.name: Landing on the Shopping page
Assert the logo of the retailer
Clicking on the close icon in the item segment
Assert that the items cannot be removed
Click on quantity in the item segment
Assert that the quantity cannot be changed

elements.name: To test the price of items in cart and in order summary

steps.name: Landing on the Shopping page
Assert the logo of the retailer
Items are listed in the shopping cart
Assert the items listed has its corresponding price
Under order summary assert your cart has total price of items in cart
Assert the delivery mode and its price
Assert the order total

elements.name: To Test the checking out of items in cart

steps.name: Landing on the Shopping page
Assert the logo of the retailer
Items are listed in the shopping cart
Click on CheckOut option
Assert it is redirected to the delivery selection page
Assert the logo of the retailer

elements.name: To test if order is placed successfully

steps.name: Landing on the Shopping page
Assert the logo of the retailer
Items are listed in the shopping cart
Click on CheckOut option
Assert it is redirected to the delivery selection page
Assert the logo of the retailer
Enter the delivery information
Enter the delivery address with <"pinCode">
Select on the <"deliveryMethod">
Assert the <"price"> of the delivery method
Assert Under order summary <"deliveryMethod"> and its <"price"> are updated correctly
Assert the total of the order summary
Click on the PROCEED TO BILLING option
Assert it is redirected to Order confirmation page
Assert that the <"successMessage"> is shown
Assert the orderId is created
Assert under Order Summary segment selected Delivery Method is listed
